### Dry-run national-team ELO seed for World Cup 2026
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/admin/elo/national-teams/seed
Content-Type: application/json
X-Admin-Key: {{admin_key}}

{
  "season": "2026",
  "dry_run": true,
  "min_coverage": 100.0
}

### Seed national-team ELO for World Cup 2026
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/admin/elo/national-teams/seed
Content-Type: application/json
X-Admin-Key: {{admin_key}}

{
  "season": "2026",
  "dry_run": false,
  "min_coverage": 100.0
}

### Audit national-team ELO coverage after seed
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/admin/elo/national-teams/coverage?season=2026
X-Admin-Key: {{admin_key}}

### Manual fallback seed input
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/admin/elo/national-teams/seed
Content-Type: application/json
X-Admin-Key: {{admin_key}}

{
  "season": "2026",
  "dry_run": true,
  "min_coverage": 100.0,
  "manual_entries": [
    {"country_name": "Brazil", "elo_raw": 2100, "rank": 1, "source_date": "manual"},
    {"country_name": "Argentina", "elo_raw": 2080, "rank": 2, "source_date": "manual"}
  ]
}
